<subSubSection pageId="4" pageNumber="5" type="material examined">
<paragraph pageId="4" pageNumber="5">Material examined.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="4" pageNumber="5">
Specimen IG-S-BL1-F5B-spB; dry state, Gallinara Island (station 3, 
<normalizedToken originalValue="Sciusciaù">Sciusciau</normalizedToken>
) 
<geoCoordinate direction="north" orientation="latitude" precision="15" value="44.02611">44°01'34&quot;N</geoCoordinate>
, 
<geoCoordinate direction="east" orientation="longitude" precision="15" value="8.229166">8°13'45&quot;E</geoCoordinate>
, depth 30 m, collected 17-06-2009. The specimen was entirely used for spicule preparations.
</paragraph>
